<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>手机端视频音频合成裁剪分离工具</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 16px;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f6fa;
      color: #222;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .tip {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background: #fff8e1;
      border: 1px solid #ffe082;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }

    .card h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      color: #333;
    }

    input, select, button {
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 15px;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
    }

    input[type="file"] {
      background: #fafafa;
    }

    button {
      margin-top: 14px;
      background: #1677ff;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    button:disabled {
      background: #999;
    }

    .secondary {
      background: #00a870;
    }

    .danger {
      background: #ff4d4f;
    }

    .result {
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 10px;
      background: #f0f7ff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    .result a {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: #1677ff;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    #log {
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      background: #111;
      color: #0f0;
      font-size: 12px;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      max-height: 180px;
      overflow: auto;
    }

    .row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .row > div {
      flex: 1;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <h1>视频音频合成 / 裁剪 / 分离工具</h1>

  <div class="tip">
    本工具在浏览器本地运行，不上传文件。首次使用需要加载 FFmpeg，可能需要等待一会儿。
    手机处理大文件会比较慢，建议使用较小的视频或音频文件。
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>1. 视频 + 音频合成</h2>

    <label>选择视频文件</label>
    <input id="mergeVideo" type="file" accept="video/*" />

    <label>选择音频文件</label>
    <input id="mergeAudio" type="file" accept="audio/*" />

    <button onclick="mergeVideoAudio()">开始合成</button>

    <div id="mergeResult" class="result"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>2. 裁剪视频或音频</h2>

    <label>选择要裁剪的文件</label>
    <input id="trimFile" type="file" accept="video/*,audio/*" />

    <div class="row">
      <div>
        <label>开始时间，秒</label>
        <input id="trimStart" type="number" placeholder="例如 5" value="0" />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label>裁剪时长，秒</label>
        <input id="trimDuration" type="number" placeholder="例如 10" value="10" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <button onclick="trimMedia()" class="secondary">开始裁剪</button>

    <div id="trimResult" class="result"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>3. 从视频中提取音频</h2>

    <label>选择视频文件</label>
    <input id="extractVideo" type="file" accept="video/*" />

    <button onclick="extractAudio()">提取音频</button>

    <div id="extractResult" class="result"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>4. 视频音画分离</h2>

    <label>选择视频文件</label>
    <input id="separateVideo" type="file" accept="video/*" />

    <button onclick="separateVideoAudio()" class="danger">
      分离为无声视频 + 音频
    </button>

    <div id="separateResult" class="result"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>运行日志</h2>
    <div id="log">等待操作...</div>
  </div>

